            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mince is cooking, chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>lime[s] </strong>in half</p><p>Combine the juice of <strong>half </strong>your<strong> lime</strong> with your <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> lime yoghurt</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1612882790150-x200.jpg",
